description: This header file defines APIs and macros for a SNMP plugin component related to the 'Broadway MIB Extension Library' in an Advanced Networking Service Container project. It declares external API functions for initialization, support checking, unloading, and memory management, which are meant to be exported for use by other modules.

methods.name: COSA_Init
methods.description: Initializes the SNMP plugin with maximum supported version and plugin info.

methods.name: COSA_Async_Init
methods.description: Performs asynchronous initialization of the SNMP plugin.

methods.name: COSA_IsObjectSupported
methods.description: Checks if a given object is supported by the plugin.

methods.name: COSA_Unload
methods.description: Unloads or cleans up the plugin.

methods.name: COSA_MemoryCheck
methods.description: Checks memory usage within the plugin.
